text: Yuanshan may refer to these locations: ==Taiwan== *Yuanshan, Yilan (員山鄉), a township of Yilan County *Yuanshan, Taipei (圓山), an area in Taipei ==People's Republic of China== ===Towns=== *Yuanshan, Guangdong (元善), in Lianping County, Guangdong *Yuanshan, Jiange County (元山), in Jiange County, Sichuan *Yuanshan, Pingchang County (元山), in Pingchang County, Sichuan
title: Yuanshan
